The prepared solar cells exhibit an only minor hysteresis, as can be seen in the JV curves in Fig. 6a. The hysteresis index (HI) of the solar cells was calculated according to2HI=∫SCOCJbwdV-JfwdVdV∫SCOCJbwdVdV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
